column1: When no record is selected and delete button is clicked the delete action is executed and no record is deleted
column26:
Description:

When no record is selected and delete button is clicked the delete action is executed and no record is deleted

Steps to reproduce:

# Navigate to Retail website
# Navigate to menu in the website
# Navigate to Returns in Sales dropdown
# Do not click on any checkbox before records
# Click on delete button 

Expected Result:

It should show an error that “no record is selected” and ask admin to select records that need to be deleted

Actual Result:

A message that “Are you sure“ is shown and action is executed

Supporting Document:

!image-20210908-200525.png|width=100%!

column1: While editing telephone field it is accepting and saving any invalid input
column26:
Description:

While editing when telephone field is updates with invalid input it saves the change without showing any error

Steps to reproduce:

# Navigate to Retail website
# Navigate to menu in the website
# Navigate to Returns in Sales dropdown
# Click on edit button in any record
# Update the the telephone field with invalid input

Expected Result:

Telephone field should not save any invalid input and show an error message 

Actual Result:

Telephone field is accepting and saving any invalid input and does not show an error message

Supporting Document:

!image-20210908-195044.png|width=100%!

column1: It is able to select date in date modified field that is before the date in date added field
column26:
Description:

It is able to accept any date in date modified field that is before the date in date added field

Steps to reproduce:

# Navigate to Retail website
# Navigate to menu in the website
# Navigate to Returns in Sales dropdown
# Select any date in Date added field 
# Select any date in Date modified field that should be before the date in Date added field

Expected Result:

Date Modified field should not accept any date before date in Date Added field 

Actual Result:

Date Modified field is accepting any date before date in Date Added field

Supporting Document:

!image-20210908-193917.png|width=100%!

column1: Admin is able to select date after current date
column26:
Description:

Date Added field and Date Modified field is accepting any date after current date

Steps to reproduce:

# Navigate to Retail website
#  Navigate to menu in the website
#  Navigate to Returns in Sales dropdown
# Navigate to Date fields in the page
# Select on Date added field and open the calendar widget and then select any date after the current date
# Select on Date modified field and open the calendar widget and then select any date after the current date

Expected Result:

Date Added field and Date Modified field should not accept any date after current date

Actual Result:

Date Added field and Date Modified field is accepting any date after current date

Supporting Document:

!image-20210908-191426.png|width=100%!
